        Initialize a CF leg with specified parameters. (Use accessors to set specific data fields for CF leg).
        Parameters:
        position - position of CF leg.
        identifier - identifier of CF leg.
        bearingFromLast - inbound course to CF leg.
        distanceFromLast - path length for CF leg.
        altRestr - Altitude restriction for leg.
        speedRestr - speed restriction for leg.
        overfly - overfly waypoint.
